Orsy  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Górowo Iławeckie, within Bartoszyce County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland, close to the border with the Kaliningrad Oblast of Russia. It lies approximately  north of Górowo Iławeckie,  north-west of Bartoszyce, and  north of the regional capital Olsztyn.
